 I was born a 2, Tolson Villas, St Marks Road, Hanwell and about two months ago a friend of my daughter took me down by car to see that house - I've been wanting to see it for years. My sister and I went once and took a Mrs Kidd - a friend of ours - died 
since - er - and we went - built up area now - but I met with a man - er - first put it in Ethel Street.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6820256\charrsid14891508 How many years did you live in the house where you were born?
