 George - my brother George - there's a little history attached to George - um - well to his school life and his business - er - and then myself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6820256\charrsid14891508 And how much was there between them do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5453887 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6820256\charrsid14891508 Oh not much - no, I think, no there wasn't muc
h altogether I think because there was only eight years - I think only about eight years between Alfred and me - the eldest one and me so I suppose there'd be what on average - er - two years or so - yes, in between.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6820256\charrsid14891508 How old was your father when you were born, have you any idea?
