Oh no, oooh no, his job was - he was at the station - his last twenty years - I think I told you - his last twenty-years was at Swiss Cottage well his job then would be from seven - er - from nine 'til 
about six - er - unless he did any of his - er - duty days for his two clerks for them to have their day off - when they were working on Sundays.
