Oh no. Er - well, after I left school - or by the time I left school - time I left Broot Street - no, er - I had an illness when I was nine - just when we were round in Laycock Street}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13249535\charrsid14891508 
