\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6820256\charrsid14891508 Did the younger children help the older ones in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5453887 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6820256\charrsid14891508 Oh, I don't know that we really needed to that much because you see we were getting that much older that we were more independent.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6820256\charrsid14891508 When you were young did the older ones help you at all with dressing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5453887 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6820256\charrsid14891508 Oh, I don't - I don't know that they - I don't know that they did anything much in that line - I think they looked - I 
think that was relied upon to mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6820256\charrsid14891508 And did you have to help them at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5453887 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6820256\charrsid14891508 I don't know that I did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6820256\charrsid14891508 Were you expected to go to bed at a certain time in your schooldays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5453887 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6820256\charrsid14891508 Well, yes, we - we didn't run about the streets like the youngst
ers do today - no - that we did - and shout and yell about - but what I do remember - er - quite a crowd of us - possibly mostly Broot Street school girls and we used to - house being about the middle of the street - we had iron railings here and the skip
p
ing rope was tied on one railing see and somebody else would stand on the other side and then we'd go off - go through the skipping rope. Until time for - er - 'til my dad came round the street and said it was time I went indoors now. With my dad - that'd
 be about half past six - that was ready for the evening meal, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6820256\charrsid14891508 Did you always go to bed at the same time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5453887 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6820256\charrsid14891508 Oh go to bed fairly regularly - oh yes, we weren't stop outs and we none of us were - um - musical - music - hall - I mean to say -
 music-hall never fascinated anybody. Oh no, we were just - an average home family.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6820256\charrsid14891508 Did your mother or anyone else put you to bed?
