Yes, we were very - mother was very particular - oh yes, we were all - oh yes, we were - we were an average - er - well, well looked after family - put it that way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6820256\charrsid14891508 Do you remember which room you used to have your meals in?
