\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5453887 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6820256\charrsid14891508 But she would bottle fruit - but not a lot - no, because we used to be able to get the fruit you see so much cheaper - those days.
