\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5453887 HB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6820256\charrsid14891508 Oh yes. Yes, yes, yes.
