Oh yes, yes. In fact, one or two of them were a little bit higher degree - er - in - er - in their schooling - oh yes - the one that I was thinking of - Wil}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13831216\charrsid14891508 l}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6820256\charrsid14891508 ie Richardson - he was the - er - nephew of one of the teachers - he was - well, thought to be more intelligent - we'll put it - than - er - anything going you know his had was up first - you know.
