From - from attending school - yes - you'd - because you learnt - as you did in those days - you learnt - well, how things should be done and - when you went to cookery or when you went to - er - laundry or anyth
ing in that way as they did - used to - I don't know what they do now. I don't think the youngsters do that sort of thing now, at all. Certainly don't do the laundry part I don't suppose.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8795008 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6820256\charrsid14891508 While you were at school did you have a part time job or any means of earning a little regular money?
