hat - another a bit of sewing - a bit of fancy work - during the hour you see - our dinner hour and - er - but I don't think we ever went up there tea time because we had a break at tea time - but I know that our hour - from one 'til two would be spent up
 there and we used to work like little niggers - we used to do all sorts of things - make all sorts of things. With crochet and that.
